node_modules/

# NOTE: news_data.json is intentionally NOT ignored.
# It is generated by recompile_html.py and committed by the
# GitHub Actions workflow so that GitHub Pages can serve it
# to the homepage JavaScript fetch() call.
# Ignoring it breaks the live feed, thumbnails, and featured brief.
